ZH: 能量释放后，粉丝们会一拥而上地争夺签名。
EN: After the energy is released, fans will rush forward to fight for autographs.

ZH: 演唱会开始后，观众们会一拥而上涌向舞台。
EN: After the concert starts, the audience will rush towards the stage.

ZH: 火灾发生时，人们会一拥而上地逃离建筑物。
EN: When a fire breaks out, people will rush out of the building.

