EN: After a gunshot, the crowd will rush into the store.

ZH: 购物优惠开放后，顾客们会一拥而上地涌入商场。
EN: When shopping discounts are offered, customers will rush into the mall.

ZH: 组长一宣布任务，队员们就会一拥而上地准备出发。
EN: As soon as the team leader announces the task, the team members will prepare to depart.

